{"tid":867501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"APPLE Special Events 公布10月30日或發佈新ipad及MAC 2018","createTime":"2018-10-18T17:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T17:06:04.000Z","uid":209242,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ca8a30a2bc8e35ff2fae23593c5bea1064c080f2","tid":867501,"uid":209242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:06:04.000Z","msg":"早前傳言 Apple 將於 10 月發佈會最後成真了。Apple 剛剛公佈將於 10 月 30  日於美國 Brooklyn 舉辦發佈會，傳聞將會推出的 iPad Pro 、  MacBook、Mac mini 及 iMac，而 iOS 12.1 及 watch OS 5.1 亦有機會同時發佈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/19/010509_059119044b22e2b85564af595db38050.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F19%2F010509_059119044b22e2b85564af595db38050.png&h=8b50255b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在 Apple 官網中按 F5 Refresh 就會看到不同造型的 Apple logo，讓人們不禁聯想到是 Apple Pencil ，看來 iPad Pro 很高機會有份了吧?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/19/010535_a662a240a3502916803f41faa37f1b4f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F19%2F010535_a662a240a3502916803f41faa37f1b4f.png&h=64df2da4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於AirPower 及新 Airpods 仍未有消息， Airpods 2 除了支援「Hey Siri」功能外，亦有傳將會配合 AirPower 提供無線充電。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/unwire.hk/2018/10/19/appel-special-events-公佈-10-月-30-日或發佈新-ipad-及-mac-2018/notebook/tablet-notebook/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F10%2F19%2Fappel-special-events-%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88-10-%E6%9C%88-30-%E6%97%A5%E6%88%96%E7%99%BC%E4%BD%88%E6%96%B0-ipad-%E5%8F%8A-mac-2018%2Fnotebook%2Ftablet-notebook%2Famp%2F&d=t4r4g0Dhr8wDwtQfLOx%2BfQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=8382c32e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/unwire.hk/2018/10/19/appel-special-events-公佈-10-月-30-日或發佈新-ipad-及-mac-2018/notebook/tablet-notebook/amp/</a>"}]}